Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.73,0:00:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.76,0:00:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger,\Nthe King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.66,0:00:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.97,0:00:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before\Nhis death drove people to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.84,0:00:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?\NIf you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.67,0:00:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.85,0:00:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men head for the\NGrand Line in pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly\Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.49,0:00:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.86,0:00:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.97,0:00:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever,\NI take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.35,0:01:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.17,0:01:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard\Nsomeone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.65,0:01:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.54,0:01:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, leave the ship, Sanji-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.71,0:01:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.04,0:01:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.38,0:02:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pearl... Cymbals!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.99,0:02:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took everything away\Nfrom that damn geezer...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.16,0:02:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that I could live...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.33,0:02:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.66,0:02:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.01,0:02:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This restaurant is that geezer's treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.01,0:02:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I can't repay the damn\Ngeezer for his kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,unless I risk my life for him, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.69,0:02:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Keep your hands off of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.53,0:02:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Battle-Axe!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.31,0:03:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Coolheaded, Coldhearted Demon;\NPirate Fleet Chief Commander Ghin"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.49,0:03:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fin's been smashed!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.33,0:03:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare that brat do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.17,0:03:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he trying to destroy the ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.51,0:03:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghin! Blow Zeff's brain out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But he saved our lives\Nby giving us 100 meals!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ghin, you son of a bitch!\N--Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.69,0:03:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't really attack\Nyou guys or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.20,0:04:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I only broke the fin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, chore boy!\NWhat do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'll sink it.\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sink this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.31,0:04:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That ain't funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering how you'd explain that...\NAre you crazy, you damn bastard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I destroy the ship,\Nthere'll be no reason for them to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you know?\NWhat do you know about
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.76,0:04:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the significance of\Nthe kindness I received?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.63,0:04:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you know\Nabout this restaurant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're gonna die for the restaurant?\NAre you stupid or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dying isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dying isn't something you\Nshould do to repay kindness!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what he saved you for!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being given life and yet dying...\Nis something that a weakling would do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then is there any other way\Nto settle this matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, you guys... Stop fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.29,0:05:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's simply disgraceful for you to fight\Namong yourselves after all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do any more reckless things\Nwhile the hostage is with us anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.97,0:05:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was unfortunate for you guys to have\Nthe Krieg Pirates as your opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burn to death with my Fire Pearls!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.82,0:05:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.83,0:05:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ghin!\N--Why... Ghin-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.84,0:05:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Pearl. Out of my way...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.01,0:05:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghin! Are you going to betray us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:06:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Don Krieg.\NHe saved our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want him to die this way.\NAt least... At least...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...please let me bury him with my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.47,0:06:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you lost your mind,\NPirate Fleet Chief Battle Commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.81,0:06:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Owner?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Owner! Please hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief Battle Commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.98,0:06:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he wasn't an underling?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.99,0:06:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that he cracked the\Nshield guy's shield... How powerful...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.16,0:06:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? It worked great...\Nmy plan to lure him out...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.00,0:06:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar! You really were going to\Nbreak the ship, weren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sanji-san!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.34,0:06:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted you to leave this ship unhurt,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.44,0:06:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it looks like that's not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.24,0:07:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let you have this restaurant\Neven if it means risking my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, at least burying you\Nwith my own hands is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my way of settling this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.29,0:07:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! Thanks. To hell with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I won't lose\Nagainst weaklings like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.64,0:07:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say\Nto our Chief Commander?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.31,0:07:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"To hell with you"? "Weaklings"?\NHow dare you run your mouth like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.65,0:07:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the Krieg Pirates,\Nthe strongest pirates in the East Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it just because you had\Nthe biggest number of pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.99,0:07:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy... You struck at\Nthe heart of the matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I was right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You son of a bitch!!\N--I'm gonna kill you!!\N--Stop mocking us!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back off!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:08:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don Krieg!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get upset when called weak,\Nthat just proves that you are weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.28,0:08:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The result will decide\Nif you're strong or weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got me. Don't get so worked up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.79,0:08:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finishing off that cook\Nis your responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.63,0:08:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of that\Nnaive idiot over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.97,0:08:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, Don Krieg.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.64,0:08:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, brat!\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you fully experience the true\Npower that conquered the East Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you that your devil fruit\Nor whatever it is means nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.99,0:08:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All your griping's getting annoying....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:09:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kick your ass. It's as simple as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming over now.\NYou just wait there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What impudence...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--This is it for that cook.\N--That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Ghin-san holds that weapon\Nin his hands, it means he's serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His nickname is... Demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if his enemy\Nis crying or screaming,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he tortures him to death mercilessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a demon who doesn't\Nhave a shred of sympathy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Sanji-san,\Nbut you can't defeat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:10:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep saying that, you small fry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.01,0:10:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You son of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.29,0:10:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I warned you...\Nthat you can't defeat me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just accept your defeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:10:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Our Chief Commander\Nis really incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:11:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crush him, Ghin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sanji!\N--Sanji! Come on!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.88,0:12:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That cook landed a blow on Ghin-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.31,0:12:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me Ghin-san\Nis gonna be defeated, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fools...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.65,0:12:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you seen with\Nyour own eyes all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghin is a coolheaded demon\Nwhom I put my trust in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.99,0:12:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly why I appointed\Nhim as the Chief Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.67,0:12:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll show his true colors soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Sanji really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course he isn't! Combining\Nthe attacks from that shield guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.65,0:12:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he must have at least 5-6 broken ribs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those skewered dumplings...\Naren't as good... as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.69,0:12:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the best\Nthe Chief Commander can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What's he doing? Is this any\Ntime to be paying attention to others?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.31,0:13:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'll kick his ass\Nwhile I have an opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.98,0:13:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.82,0:13:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't overexert yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.84,0:13:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!!\NDo you really intend to fight me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.01,0:13:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Intend to fight you?\NI don't need to do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's needed is\Na means to kill. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.68,0:13:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's the force that humans have.\NRemember it, you damn monkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! If you take a monkey\Nlightly, it'll scratch you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.81,0:14:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! His bones\Nare shattered by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.98,0:14:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.98,0:14:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! If only he hadn't taken\Nthe damage from the shield guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.82,0:14:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's taken at least 10 hits\Nof those iron balls by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.66,0:14:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really do whatever\Nyou want... you small fry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn... He's really strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.68,0:14:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finish you off now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.68,0:14:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't struggle any more...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.82,0:14:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?! Pity?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.85,0:14:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Ghin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.14,0:15:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! He can no longer bear even\Nthe shock from his own attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.66,0:15:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--All right!\N--That's our Ghin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.33,0:15:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... damn... bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.79,0:16:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.29,0:16:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't... Don Krieg...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?\N--I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.31,0:16:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it, Don Krieg!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.98,0:16:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghin...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.98,0:16:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't... kill this man...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.66,0:16:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.99,0:16:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was... it was the first time for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.50,0:16:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when I'm down and out,\NI won't take charity from others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.67,0:16:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this food away now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.84,0:16:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop whining and eat it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To me, anyone who's\Nhungry is a customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.28,0:17:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'm not a customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.95,0:17:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand how a hungry\Nperson feels more than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.29,0:17:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can die for your pride if you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.79,0:17:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if you eat and survive,\Ndon't you think there's a future for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.97,0:17:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... Thank you... I thought\NI'd die. I thought I was done...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.98,0:17:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious... Delicious...\NI've never eaten food so delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.99,0:17:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's damn delicious, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... You're gonna get yelled at,\Nbecause you fed me free, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.84,0:18:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no proof, so there's no\Nreason for me to be yelled at.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.28,0:18:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one had treated me\Nso kindly before...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.45,0:18:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I can't... kill this man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.79,0:18:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back any time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.79,0:18:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know... I don't intend to betray you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think what we've done up until\Nnow is wrong or anything, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.64,0:18:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still respect your power\Nand I appreciate you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.64,0:18:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was really happy when you\Nput your trust in my strength
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.24,0:18:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and appointed me as\Nthe Chief Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.65,0:18:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I've followed your orders\Nand I will from here on as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.65,0:18:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.82,0:18:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't kill... just this one person!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.27,0:19:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don Krieg... If circumstances\Nallow... is there any way...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.94,0:19:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is there any way you'd let this ship...\Nthis restaurant off the hook...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.28,0:19:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if defying my orders wasn't enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.58,0:19:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,now you're giving me a lecture?!\NWhat's the meaning of this craziness?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.62,0:19:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How disappointing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.62,0:19:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morality... Sympathy...\NI hate those kinds of things the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.96,0:19:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I always say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move away, guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.97,0:19:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don! That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.98,0:19:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M... MH5!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.81,0:19:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the strongest poison gas weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.31,0:19:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--Poison gas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.32,0:19:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ahh! Mask!\N--Put the mask on!\N--Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.09,0:19:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We'll be killed, too!\N--To use a weapon like that...\N--That's despicable, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.99,0:20:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what's gonna\Nhappen when you use that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop whining about stupid stuff,\Nyou fools! This is a battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Winning is the only goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.17,0:20:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Foul play? Dirty?\NWhat's wrong with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.01,0:20:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Might makes right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.81,0:20:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what means we take,\Nthe result is everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.18,0:20:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using poison gas or whatever...\NWinning is all that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.02,0:20:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a horrible bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.70,0:20:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Throw that gas mask away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.37,0:20:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're no longer one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:21:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you shoot poison gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.65,0:21:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop scampering about, anchor boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghin! You don't have to listen\Nto what that weakling says!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.51,0:21:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kick his ass now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.01,0:21:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mock Don Krieg!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.52,0:21:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the strongest man.\NYou can't defeat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.19,0:21:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to your senses, you idiot!\NThat man is trying to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I deserve it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.36,0:21:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...since I couldn't fulfill my role,\Nshamelessly losing to emotion...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.03,0:21:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... This is a\Nwell-deserved punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.37,0:21:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ghin!\N--Why... Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.98,0:22:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! So you showed your pride\Nat the end... But it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.65,0:22:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die together with that cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.32,0:22:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deadly Poison Gas Bomb... M... H... 5!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.00,0:22:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dive into the sea!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.33,0:22:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Owner! Get inside the restaurant!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.84,0:22:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me borrow those.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.51,0:22:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji! Ghin! Use these!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.68,0:22:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Chore boy!\N--Now for mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.68,0:22:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! Everyone dived into the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.52,0:22:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy... Oh, boy... Oh, boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.03,0:23:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was little, I had\Na vision of a treasure map
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.28,0:23:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I always searched\Nfor that miraculous place
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.22,0:23:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before someone else could\Nbeat me to it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.93,0:23:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the world is going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.41,0:23:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before I can even attain my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.41,0:23:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then take me to the time\Nwhen I knew nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.49,0:24:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that my memories won't fade
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.14,0:24:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you whose\Ngraveyard this place is!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.48,0:24:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't stop my ambition\Nwith a silly weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.15,0:24:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come you don't flinch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.65,0:24:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know?\NAre you stupid or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.32,0:24:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say? Say that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.15,0:24:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Are you stupid or what?\N--Don't repeat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.65,0:24:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who told me to say\Nthat again. How selfish you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.66,0:24:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.99,0:24:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I Won't Die!\NFierce Battle, Luffy vs. Krieg!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.50,0:24:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.36,0:24:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
